      "description": "Context: The demo includes a log shipping path (Promtail → Loki) to support basic operational triage.\n\nFocus: Confirm that the log pipeline is actively ingesting data in the current window.\n\nImplementation: Backed by `count_over_time` over 5 minutes on `{job=\"dockerlogs\"}` and aggregated via `sum()`.",
